static_fields.name: Discover Divido Rubber | Minase Watches | Made in Japan
static_fields.description: Divido rubber is powered with a high quality Swiss movement, every steel parts is hand-polished with the Sallaz (sarazu) technique.

hasVariant.name: Divido Rubber - White
hasVariant.description: Divido's unique design is inspired by the Japanese 3-dimentional puzzle. The dial seems to be floating inside the case, suspended below the box-type sapphire crystal. Handmade in Japan and finished with the rare sallaz polishing technique.
